h \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4608,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/09\/salaam-alaykum-rahmatullah-barakatuhu\/","url_meta":{"origin":39739,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Greetings: Peace, mercy, and blessings upon you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Imran ibn Husayn reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cPeace be upon you.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cTen good deeds.\u201d Then, another man came to the Prophet, saying, \u201cPeace be upon you and the mercy of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cTwenty good deeds.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2067,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/11\/tashahhud-sitting-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":39739,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: What to say when sitting in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: While praying behind the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, we were saying, \u201cPeace be upon Allah, peace be upon this person.\u201d The Prophet told us one day, \"Verily, Allah Himself is Peace. When one of you sits in prayer, let him say,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15419,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/gabriel-greet-peace\/","url_meta":{"origin":39739,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jibreel: Angel Gabriel greets you with peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said to her, \u201cO Aisha, here is the Angel Gabriel to greet you with peace.\" Aisha said, \"And upon him be peace, the mercy of Allah, and His blessings. You see what I do not see.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6249,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11575,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/greeting-visit-qabr-madinah\/","url_meta":{"origin":39739,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ziyarah: Greeting the Prophet at his grave","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNone of you greets me with peace (at his grave) except Allah returns my spirit, that I may return his greeting of peace.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2041 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"h